title: Mishba - Friedrichstrasse
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, American, International, Fast food, Salad bar, Take-out, Turkish, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Fast food counter in the underground station; enter at Georgenstrasse. Has clearly marked vegan choices, including salad, baked potato, and a burrito. You can create your own meal by picking and choosing the base and toppings.
